to the Library of Congress

00:08:07.020 --> 00:08:09.720
for the first time in 1986.

00:08:09.720 --> 00:08:13.590
And I think -- I remember
writing in my journal there is

00:08:13.590 --> 00:08:17.510
so much information
and knowledge here

00:08:17.510 --> 00:08:20.650
and I already have quickly
discovered that things

00:08:20.650 --> 00:08:24.850
