00:09:55.680 --> 00:09:58.650 position:56%
They are all brilliant like no joke,

00:09:58.650 --> 00:10:01.790
like really exceptionally
brilliant and bright.

00:10:01.790 --> 00:10:06.460
They volunteer like
their time at time

00:10:06.460 --> 00:10:08.070
