00:28:13.960 --> 00:28:18.560
We've never -- I don't think we
have ever had an organizational

00:28:18.560 --> 00:28:20.570
discussion actually.

00:28:20.570 --> 00:28:23.430
I don't think we've ever
said, here are the things.

00:28:23.430 --> 00:28:27.790
We just kind of worked and we
say, Chris is good at this.

