00:29:27.650 --> 00:29:36.600
and sound and the worlds and
to allow that to be a school

00:29:36.600 --> 00:29:40.440
and to keep asking, you know,
what is it that I'm hearing?

00:29:40.440 --> 00:29:41.980
What are the projects
that I'm seeing?

00:29:41.980 --> 00:29:44.580
How is this -- you should
just go as a listener, I mean,

00:29:44.580 --> 00:29:47.850
going back to what Chris
said about humility.

00:29:47.850 --> 00:29:51.160
So I don't -- this is not going to
answer the question about hierarchy

00:29:51.160 --> 00:29:56.940
but I feel like that's all I can
-- that's what I know or how I know

00:29:56.940 --> 00:30:01.040
