00:30:35.180 --> 00:30:38.670
an institution, fundraising
is not a problem.

00:30:38.670 --> 00:30:40.370
Talking to donors is not a problem.

00:30:40.370 --> 00:30:41.670
I wear multiple hats.

00:30:41.670 --> 00:30:43.480
I can speak to anybody.

00:30:43.480 --> 00:30:45.390
I could be very English
when I need to be.

00:30:45.390 --> 00:30:46.690
I could be very [laughter] --

00:30:46.690 --> 00:30:51.490
I could be extremely Nigerian
when I need to [laughter].

00:30:51.490 --> 00:30:54.010
You know, I can guide people
very quickly to their checkbooks

00:30:54.010 --> 00:30:56.240
when I need them to [laughter].

00:30:56.240 --> 00:30:59.480
So and I have no -- this
