00:31:07.010 --> 00:31:09.910
But I'm not even asking
things for other people,

00:31:09.910 --> 00:31:16.460
I'm asking for the support of
an institution, of a thing,

00:31:16.460 --> 00:31:21.250
of an entity that is almost
alive that is beyond individuals.

00:31:21.250 --> 00:31:23.420
It's really not about
individuals at all.

00:31:23.420 --> 00:31:27.030
I'm not asking for money for
Tsitsi's book or Mukoma's book.

00:31:27.030 --> 00:31:32.580 position:56%
I'm asking for something that should
exist already and that I'm asking

00:31:32.580 --> 00:31:34.910
for it is already out of sync.

00:31:34.910 --> 00:31:37.260
So I have no difficulty.

00:31:37.260 --> 00:31:40.220
There is no hierarchy but
we -- this is the thing.

00:31:40.220 --> 00:31:42.710
We trust Kwame implicitly.

00:31:42.710 --> 00:31:44.680
And this is why I think
also articulate in there.

00:31:44.680 --> 00:31:45.980
There is no ego involved.

00:31:45.980 --> 00:31:48.790
It's not like well, you didn't
mention that I did all this stuff.

00:31:48.790 --> 00:31:51.070
You didn't mention [laughter]
-- in fact, you know,

00:31:51.070 --> 00:31:53.230
Kwame is always trying to
deflect attention and credit.

00:31:53.230 --> 00:31:56.110
And we're always trying to
like push it in his way.

00:31:56.110 --> 00:32:00.280 position:56%
But we entrust -- so even yesterday,
we sat down, the three of us --

00:32:00.280 --> 00:32:02.720
Matthew, Kwame and I -- we
were having a cup of coffee

00:32:02.720 --> 00:32:04.190
