signing a book and someone says,

01:01:16.830 --> 01:01:19.620
"What book made you
want to be a writer?"

01:01:19.620 --> 01:01:24.400
He will say Safir's inner life
made my inner life possible.

01:01:24.400 --> 01:01:26.830
