inward, blue, and enough.

01:10:10.980 --> 01:10:13.190
I imagined childhood a swamp.

01:10:13.190 --> 01:10:18.720
Wet, my small self, nappy
hair doubled by cockleburs,

01:10:18.720 --> 01:10:22.410
easy name [inaudible]
spineless and clean,

01:10:22.410 --> 01:10:29.100
