from the doorposts.

01:13:10.610 --> 01:13:13.930
Too many chickens are
coming home to roost.

01:13:13.930 --> 01:13:17.060
And it is not the storm.

01:13:17.060 --> 01:13:20.590
It is not the August
or September hurricane.

01:13:20.590 --> 01:13:24.970
It is not the storm that's driving
home all the angry of heart,

